In the MATTER OF Christopher J. BASNER, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 010612008) R-8 September Term 2016
D-158-16
079461 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 02, 2018

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented to the Court on the petition of respondent, CHRISTOPHER J. BASNER , for review of the decision of the Disciplinary Review Board in DRB 16-341, and good cause appearing;

It is ORDERED that the petition for review is denied.
